metadata.name: Brazilian Favelas AI 2
metadata.description:
Brazilian Favelas AI are AI (artificial intelligence) generated art images representing a social aspect of brazilian culture, the brazilian favelas. Each set of images represent an evolutive exploratory iteration of the work. Where each iteration explores different styles, colors and concepts. The goal is to: 
1 - Bring an excluded topic to an art project. 
2 - Explore the limits and possibilities of the technology in the art realm. 
3 - Evaluate the impact of the artist cultural baggage on the resulting work.
